BREAKING: Progress Emerges Winner Of Nigeria Idol Season By Samuel Abulude, Lagos Progress has emerged winner of the popular music reality show, Nigerian Idol Season 7. The amiable budding singer, who emerged as one of finalists, defeated fellow contestant, Zadok, to clinch the grand prize of N100m. The Nigerian Idol, which had the judges namely Obi Asika, music stars, Simi, D’Banj and Omawumi, was a keenly contested competition with attracted millions of viewership. The finally week garnered about 45 million votes to determine the eventual winner. Details Later…